Main Views Folder

Location:

resources/views/

Inside this folder we create 4 subfolders:

views
 ├── admin
 ├── site
 ├── layouts
 └── auth
2️⃣ Layout Files

These are common templates used by multiple pages.

Location:

resources/views/layouts/

Files:

layouts
 ├── admin.blade.php
 └── site.blade.php
Example: admin.blade.php
